{"tid":1065304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★陳茂波網誌：投放5億元，向每所資助中學提供支援，設立「IT創新實驗室」","createTime":"2019-03-17T07:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T10:10:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"10d6ec27f65ddf353d47b0fb19d32915a2dbda51","tid":1065304,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:00:34.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波表示，預算案部分措施是源於與年青人或小朋友交流，體會到他們的需要，由他們的訴求催生的。<br />\n<br />\n他在網誌透露，他到訪過的中小學，曾向他介紹科普教育情況，亦有中學生向他遞交建議書，希望政府增撥資源，加強STEM主題的學習支援。這些意見促使他落實在未來3年，投入合共5億元，向每所資助中學提供100萬元支援，設立「IT創新實驗室」，讓學生在傳統課堂學習以外，參加更多與資訊科技相關的課外活動。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波又指，預算案同時有措施，投放3億元加快發展「空間數據共享平台」，以便在未來分階段推出全港3D數碼地圖。他形容，這個地理空間數據庫，將彷如「超級市場」般，讓大家容易找到相關資源，有利開發應用服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448111-20190317.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448111-20190317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2F5ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=38b440b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448111-20190317.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b9ae35fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448111-20190317.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4720d989f96ac83519009bfb0dbe6c5f942c95b5","tid":1065304,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:01:23.000Z","msg":"$4000用FAX提交不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2348f9c7945a40d8baced3e3426ce740854390b0","tid":1065304,"uid":15984,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"ON9, 又投放搞創新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces